namespace Pizza

features
	Pizza {abstract}	
		mandatory
			Topping {abstract}	
				or
					Salami
					Ham
					Mozzarella
			Size	
				alternative
					Normal
					Big
			Dough	
				alternative
					Neapolitan
					Sicilian

		optional
			CheesyCrust

constraints
	CheesyCrust & Sicilian => Big
	Neapolitan => !Salami & !Ham
	Neapolitan & Pizza & !Size | Sicilian